stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> LoggedOut
  LoggedOut --> SurveyList: login ok
  SurveyList --> ActiveSession: choose survey
  ActiveSession --> Resolving: answer changed
  Resolving --> ActiveSession: same schema / ok
  Resolving --> AtomicRecovered: compatible version change
  Resolving --> RolledBack: incompatible version change
  Resolving --> ConflictFlagged: zombie/orphan detected
  AtomicRecovered --> ActiveSession
  RolledBack --> ActiveSession
  ConflictFlagged --> ActiveSession: user continues from stable node
  ActiveSession --> Submitted: send enabled + tapped
  Submitted --> [*]
